rown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本無反擊手段"},{"pid":"d51f7ffde5768cf0d7945981ba710fa328e5f8c2","tid":1380962,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a7fb1e415c3dfbf0f600dff2065a2bad379bcd1","tid":1380962,"uid":272467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"少少意見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要退但唔好潰不成軍"},{"pid":"18bf98805ef467325a3fe59f78c37ec927000557","tid":1380962,"uid":24814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c5befc6aafb9a08ca81bb61662a396c293dbff","tid":1380962,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9c9d0c33512501f65edfc09e435645b672defb6","tid":1380962,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"留意返，港澳扮咁講即係支持黑社會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381180</a>"},{"pid":"79dded0acbdc16a5300b404ca024998f4ad76bbe","tid":1380962,"uid":42007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"假若想多戰線，我地就更應該發揮be water嘅威力 。7.1當日空前成功，亦成功發揮be water。如果大家仲記得，當時立會爆緊，有手足成功喺金紫荊升黑旗。反觀今日，今日大家好似係一潭卡咗喺中區嘅死水咁。警總、政總係可以完全冇人理，更加莫講其他政府地標。大家過份陣地戰，情況只會好似5年前咁。<br />\n大家成日講敵進我退，但你要be water，仲要敵駐我擾，令敵人疲於奔命！"},{"pid":"ad2bff1c8a658e4ca4a7c0d83aca37ad579ce8f1","tid":1380962,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fb68e8aef739499608e3d0a7759191ff83aed56","tid":1380962,"uid":168339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"人多應該打番走佢地先撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次咁捉 好快無哂手足"},{"pid":"47aa3a2191f2c589cdb0d359b7610582b1c6d2af","tid":1380962,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c42709111355db2b63c6a2d7419aec4b34e8e","tid":1380962,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde632bf6b9496cdc5ee4e99d8f761108872e235","tid":1380962,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"289d17de6cc84a438ba56957191152a05731e716","tid":1380962,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab74cb7277b69fd2a9bfdb213f901678b8007d3e","tid":1380962,"uid":289213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1468023ed9bc51bc57d79521e6f79e40a93df82a","tid":1380962,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dd59bd6dee598b1f8f26cc1525a7f5834af8d33","tid":1380962,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7d5cc9e002e45c849fe55cd0c7f6225a2047a8d2","tid":1380962,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"5/8 全港大罷工"},{"pid":"1fdee427a6ab056307917f2b440c30ec18d1af0c","tid":1380962,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"[中、上、西環地理戰術]728撤退慘敗之反撃可行性分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381396</